    "It captures seasonal variations and various driving scenarios, encompassing freeways, residential areas, tunnels, and vegetationrich zones, utilizing four HDL-32E LiDARs.",
    "Nevertheless, the uniform configuration of the LiDARs still poses a challenge.",
    "In contrast, LIBRE [15] provides a driving dataset along with a separate distance error report for 12 LiDARs, detailing performance under diverse weather conditions.",
    "It is essential to note that each sequence in LIBRE features only a single LiDAR.",
    "Moreover, the dataset does not provide insights into LiDAR odometry on platforms with aggressive motions since it only involves stationary LiDAR-equipped vehicles in artificially controlled weather conditions.The previously mentioned LiDAR datasets collected with mapping-car systems have limitations in roll and pitch angle variations."
